parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The moisture/condensation issue in the headlights can cause the lights to dim or fail, leading to reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents while driving at night.
symptoms: moisture or condensation inside the headlight assembly
difficulty seeing while driving at night.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rear brake light issue can cause reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Rear brake lights remaining on while moving or parked.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear suspension can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The service rear axle message is displayed
the rear end of the vehicle shakes or wobbles
abnormal noises are heard from the rear of the vehicle
and the vehicle may stall or lose motive power.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Stabilitrak and Traction Control System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Stabilitrak and traction control system can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The Stabilitrak and traction control warning lights are illuminated
the vehicle may stall or lose motive power
and the service Stabili-trak and traction control messages are displayed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake warning light is illuminated
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the vehicle takes longer to stop than usual
and the ABS warning light is illuminated.
